\par\pard\plain \sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Although Sarah was conflicted when Evan proposed, she accepted. Her father was disappointed that Sarah decided to abandon her master plan, and instead, follow Evan to Chicago. He gave her a month to change her mind before cutting off his financial support.<!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>}
