\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b1\i0\cf6 Sarah:}{\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::3> In contrast to Evan, Sarah remained conflicted. She felt paralyzed by this tug-of-war between her mind and her heart. She felt paralyzed by this choice between the two most important men in her life \endash  her father and Evan. She was going to hurt one of the men she loved, no matter what her decision was.<!$Scr_Cs::3><!$Scr_Ps::2>}
